Title: 'The dream of cancer '
DateModified: '2019-03-13'
DatePublished: '2019-03-13'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-dream-of-cancer
SetInCountry: Egypt
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Ahmedbahaa Attia
AuthorCountry: Egypt
Text: 'One day my friend went to visit the doctor who told him after fixing him that
  he has a cancer my dearly friend wished to visit the world before he die so he was
  very sad not because he will die absolutely but because his dream killed about visiting
  the world . He decided to achieve his dream although his doctor prevented him to
  do that but he didn''t take in his mind he made a list of a number of countries
  that he should visit in his unknown trip . The first country was France he went
  to Paris to see the sights and the romantic city he was very happy to do this but
  he forgot that he has a cancer and this master wait him . In his trip to Paris he
  saw a beautiful girl called Samantha his heart moved when he saw her so he talked
  ho her and after 3month they came friends the surprise was that his new girlfriend
  will

  Continue his trip with him.

  The next trip was to England to the the city whish he dreamed to see this city was
  very beautiful and his girlfriend made him more happy he meeted very things and
  learned more things he thought me the right mean to happiness . But finally he die
  but his trip didn''t die'
